Package com.github.kennedyoliveira.pastebin4j

Classes for interacting with the PasteBin API.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AccountCredentials
    Represents the account credentials for logging into the API and fetch informations.
    GuestPaste
    This class exists just to create guest pastes even when the AccountCredentials has its AccountCredentials.userName and AccountCredentials.password filled.
    Paste
    Represents a paste.
    Paste.Builder
    Paste builder static inner class.
    PasteBin
    Core class to interact with the PasteBin API.
    UserInformation
    User information fetched from the API.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AccountType
    Represents the possible account types.
    PasteExpiration
    Represents a experation for a Paste
    PasteHighLight
    All the supported syntax highlights currently available.
    PasteVisibility
    The possible visibility that a Paste can has.
